body:
Your Rotation: If you could make your OWN rotation using any nebula map what would be in it?

*You can choose any maps! New and old or removed maps
 * Remember choose NEBULA maps




Example:
1. Quintus
2. Justice III
3. Axis
4. Gladiator
5. Rendezvous
6. Venomous TDM
etc....

I mean Avicus before the Avicore Update. It was my fav time on the server, cuz this were the only maps and you could learn how these maps work. After some time you have your strategics for them and it was more fun everytime you played the map. Sadly now half of the maps from the list are removed :'(
